    • Teams must win at least one tournament to be eligible to win the Club Championship.
    • Teams must finish top 8 at least two tournaments to be eligible for Club Championship rankings and prize pool.
    • No points are awarded for placements below 8th in any title (excluding StarCraft II).
    • If an organization has more than 1 entry in a tournament, only the best placing entry grant Club Points.
